(2186, '<p>Atelier cr&eacute;ation d&#39;email en anglais.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mise en situation professionnelle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Request&nbsp;:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&laquo;&nbsp;Good morning sir.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I would like to know if you can handle Macintosh related issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Because I have a macbook pro and it seems that my battery is not charging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I cannot use my macbook no more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Could you help me? Any advice?&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Support Answer:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hi, I&rsquo;m Farid from [BRAND],</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It looks like your battery has a problem.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>This can come from the power supplier,</li>\r\n	<li>Or the internal battery connexion</li>\r\n	<li>Or it can come from the battery itself</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>You can bring your computer at [BRAND] shop for a complete and professional look up by one of our expert.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is the address&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of our expert will take a look at your machine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This will allow us to assess the exact issue so we can provide a quick fix for your computer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let me know if you have any question.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best regards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Farid Chaan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Position]</p>\r\n', '2016-11-01 23:00:00', 144),
